text: The Fifth Element () is a 1997 English-language French science-fiction action movie directed and co-written by Luc Besson. It stars Bruce Willis, Gary Oldman, and Milla Jovovich. The Fifth Element received mainly positive reviews. ==Notes== ==References== == Other websites == * * Category:1997 action movies Category:1997 science fiction movies Category:Movies directed by Luc Besson Category:French action movies Category:French science fiction movies
